ğŸŒ How the Web Works (Basic Flow)

1. User enters a **URL** in the browser
2. Browser requests data from a **server**
3. **DNS** converts domain name â†’ IP address
4. Server processes request
5. Server sends response (HTML, CSS, JS, data)
6. Browser renders the website

ğŸ” **HTTPS** uses SSL/TLS encryption to keep data secure

